materiaux:
Supplies
  • you’ll need a ball any will work and really depends on how u like it . 2 bungee cords, a draw string bag, and string of zip ties, to make a slot for the bungee cord to pass,

etapes.html:
1. Step 1: Put the Ball Into the Bag

Étapes :

  1. the ball should be just in the middle of the bag, doesn’t have to be perfect, just needs to be easy to work with just tie or zip tie the two ends to make a tight shape and thread the string to the zipties

2. Step 2: Hang It Up

Étapes :

  1. the easy way to do this is to loop it around a thick branch from a tree, but if u want just get an eyebolt to pass the cord through, if the eye bolt is to small, put rope around it for a loop that is bigger. Have fun with your new boxing gear
